161
00:09:32,550 --> 00:09:33,440
Isn't it cute?

162
00:09:38,790 --> 00:09:39,870
This is you.

163
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,320
This is me.

164
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:43,960
