180
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:33,480
- Is it good?
- Yes, it is.

181
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,670
Do you know how long it took me

182
00:10:36,670 --> 00:10:37,910
to make this cake?

183
00:10:38,750 --> 00:10:39,630
Two hours?

184
00:10:40,910 --> 00:10:41,720
Three hours?

185
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,270
Two hours.

186
00:10:44,390 --> 00:10:48,150
It didn't take long to make the cake,
but a long time to conceive the shape.

187
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:50,550
That cake is

188
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:52,030
round.

189
00:10:53,030 --> 00:10:54,120
Nonsense.

190
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,030
Li Nai!

191
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:10,440
I'm coming.

192
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:18,270
What's going on?

193
00:11:18,510 --> 00:11:20,270
