to the ground?

195
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:25,150
Just tell me why you came to me.

196
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:26,720
I need to ask for leave.

197
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:28,390
I meant to come early
and arrange everything.

198
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:29,840
But since you're here...

199
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:31,000
I'll leave the restaurant to you.

200
00:11:31,030 --> 00:11:32,750
- Just get going. Go.
- I'm off then.

201
00:11:32,910 --> 00:11:33,720
Bye.

202
