00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:35,550
and the Alliance together.

274
00:15:39,630 --> 00:15:40,840
I got it, Mr. Jiang.

275
00:15:41,550 --> 00:15:42,870
I'll tell them your idea.

276
00:15:58,790 --> 00:16:00,720
You've followed me all the way.
Will you stop it?

277
00:16:08,550 --> 00:16:09,510
Cao Liang!

278
00:16:09,910 --> 00:16:13,080
Let me tell you.
I don't care what my grandpa tells you.

279
00:16:13,080 --> 00:16:15,550
I won't like you or cooperate with you.

280
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:20,120
Miss Jiang, don't rush to reject me.

281
00:16:20,720 --> 00:16:23,030
Mr. Jiang is looking for a suitable man
for you in the Alliance.

282
00:16:23,105 --> 00:16:24,550
How can there be any good man
in the Alliance?

283
00:16:24,670 --> 00:16:26,240
They're merely some good-for-nothing

284
00:16:26,510 --> 00:16:28,080
who covet the Jiang family's position.

285
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:31,320
Don't make it sound like you're not.

286
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:33,030
Of course I'm different.

287
00:16:33,320 --> 00:16:35,510
I have Cao's Fish which is
only second to Xijiangyue.

288
00:16:35,630 --> 00:16:36,870
I'm not after your position.

289
00:16:37,390 --> 00:16:39,240
But if you need help,

290
00:16:39,960 --> 00:16:41,120
I have enough experience.

291
00:16:41,550 --> 00:16:42,720
Another man may be an appendage,

292
00:16:42,870 --> 00:16:44,120
but we can be partners.

293
00:16:46,240 --> 00:16:47,080
Are you done?

294
00:16:48,390 --> 00:16:51,150
You're obviously calculating.

295
00:16:51,790 --> 00:16:53,440
Since you covet nothing,

296
00:16:53,440 --> 00:16:55,600
why are you badgering me?

297
00:16:55,600 --> 00:16:57,630
Of course it's because I like you.

298
00:16:59,360 --> 00:17:00,480
Don't worry.

299
00:17:00,790 --> 00:17:02,480
I won't ask you to cooperate.

300
00:17:02,790 --> 00:17:05,160
Instead, I'm at your service anytime.
Like, now.

301
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:17,240
You're...

302
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:26,440
Cao Liang, didn't you say
you wanted to see my room?

303
00:17:26,440 --> 00:17:27,440
What are you waiting for?

304
00:17:32,680 --> 00:17:34,240
- Mr. Jiang.
- It's okay.

305
00:17:34,310 --> 00:17:35,880
Xiu is always so willful.

306
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:37,000
Just let her be.

307
00:17:41,110 --> 00:17:42,640
I have a visitor here.

308
00:17:42,640 --> 00:17:43,720
I won't see you off then.

309
00:17:44,680 --> 00:17:45,400
Never mind.

310
00:17:46,480 --> 00:17:47,750
When the plan comes out,

311
00:17:48,200 --> 00:17:49,000
I'll tell you at once.

312
00:17:58,960 --> 00:18:00,590
It's a deal then.

313
00:18:02,030 --> 00:18:03,160
Thank you for your hard work.

314
00:18:03,350 --> 00:18:04,400
See you next time.

315
00:18:04,400 --> 00:18:05,830
Mind how you go. Bye.

316
00:18:15,270 --> 00:18:17,240
Why are you here? Where's Wang?

317
00:18:17,350 --> 00:18:18,640
I asked him not to come.

318
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:20,680
I'm worried you may feel sick
after drinking,

319
00:18:20,790 --> 00:18:21,830
and he can't take good care of you.

320
00:18:22,070 --> 00:18:23,720
You've worried too much.

321
00:18:24,070 --> 00:18:26,000
Just leave this to Wang.

322
00:18:26,750 --> 00:18:27,920
I can't be reassured.

323
00:18:29,480 --> 00:18:30,240
Xuyang,

324
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:33,270
will you return to Shengting tonight?

325
00:18:33,550 --> 00:18:35,400
I've got something to show you.

326
00:18:35,640 --> 00:18:36,680
I won't go back for now.

327
00:18:36,920 --> 00:18:38,270
I need to go to Li Park.

328
00:18:38,350 --> 00:18:39,350
It's my grandpa's arrangement.

329
00:18:39,550 --> 00:18:41,720
You still have to socialize later?

330
00:18:41,920 --> 00:18:43,920
Yes, it's for a private business.

331
00:18:44,110 --> 00:18:46,400
With the daughter of Mr. Zhang
from Zhengguang.

332
00:18:50,880 --> 00:18:53,000
Did you not use the additional card
I gave you lately?

333
00:18:54,000 --> 00:18:56,310
I've never received any message
of your spending.

334
00:18:58,070 --> 00:18:58,880
Yes, I did.

335
00:19:00,310 --> 00:19:03,640
Maybe the messages are blocked
as trash messages.

336
00:19:05,070 --> 00:19:06,640
Anyway, whatever you wanna buy,

337
00:19:06,640 --> 00:19:07,640
just buy it

338
00:19:07,960 --> 00:19:09,030
as you like.

339
00:19:14,270 --> 00:19:15,070
I've got things to do.

340
00:19:15,750 --> 00:19:16,720
Take care when you go home.

341
00:19:28,900 --> 00:19:31,220
(Your credit card spent 1,032 yuan
in a maternal and infant store.)

342
00:19:45,060 --> 00:19:46,900
(Is it normal to miss my boyfriend
after just seeing him?)

343
00:19:48,580 --> 00:19:50,300
(Is it normal to miss my boyfriend
after ten minutes?)

344
00:19:53,180 --> 00:19:55,860
(What if I want to be with my love
every day?)

345
00:20:05,350 --> 00:20:08,350
Xiu has stopped loving me.
What should I do?

346
00:20:08,350 --> 00:20:10,920
Li Nai, what should I do?

347
00:20:11,960 --> 00:20:14,160
I've never been to her room.

348
00:20:14,960 --> 00:20:16,240
How can he...

349
00:20:18,070 --> 00:20:19,750
Don't wake Li Jidong up.

350
00:20:19,960 --> 00:20:20,920
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

351
00:20:23,550 --> 00:20:27,000
Xiu doesn't love me anymore.
What should I do?

352
00:20:27,270 --> 00:20:28,550
It serves you right.

353
00:20:29,070 --> 00:20:31,550
It was fine for you to be a spy.
Why did you ghost her?

354
00:20:31,920 --> 00:20:33,070
Well, you ghosted her. Fine.

355
00:20:33,070 --> 00:20:34,640
Why did you reject her

356
00:20:34,640 --> 00:20:37,000
when Jiang Ziqing tried to set you two up?

357
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:38,640
If I were with Xiu,

358
00:20:39,440 --> 00:20:42,070
my sister and Jiang Xuyang wouldn't
trust me for sure.

359
00:20:42,720 --> 00:20:44,480
They'd take precautions against me.

360
00:20:45,510 --> 00:20:47,000
Why don't you come back?

361
00:20:47,550 --> 00:20:50,480
Just as well Eating at Dusk is aiming
to be the No. 1 of next year.

362
00:20:50,830 --> 00:20:53,110
You can apologize to Jiang Xiu.
I'll help you.

363
00:20:53,790 --> 00:20:55,830
Do you think she'll forgive me?

364
00:20:57,270 --> 00:20:58,640
I'll ask Jiang Jie to help you.

365
00:21:01,110 --> 00:21:03,440
No, no, no.

366
00:21:03,640 --> 00:21:05,750
Then you can continue being the mole

367
00:21:05,750 --> 00:21:07,310
and watch Jiang Xiu

368
00:21:07,310 --> 00:21:09,880
live a happy life with another man.

369
00:21:10,160 --> 00:21:11,160
Li Nai, listen to me.

370
00:21:11,160 --> 00:21:12,550
Hear me out, Li Nai.

371
00:21:13,510 --> 00:21:14,240
Here's the thing.

372
00:21:15,200 --> 00:21:17,640
The Alliance Meeting is about to begin.

373
00:21:18,160 --> 00:21:20,160
I'm thinking if Jiang Xuyang
has any plan,

374
00:21:20,160 --> 00:21:21,750
I can let you know in the first place.

375
00:21:21,920 --> 00:21:23,030
Besides, you know,

376
00:21:23,030 --> 00:21:26,400
the Alliance Meeting and Jiang Ziqing's
birthday party will be held together.

377
00:21:26,400 --> 00:21:27,920
Be held together?

378
00:21:28,720 --> 00:21:31,350
It's such a huge thing,
but you didn't tell me until now.

379
00:21:31,880 --> 00:21:34,680
What's wrong? Got any plans?

380
00:21:35,030 --> 00:21:36,270
Not really.

381
00:21:38,310 --> 00:21:38,830
Oh no.

382
00:21:39,680 --> 00:21:41,880
Yes, I do. I have a plan.

383
00:21:42,110 --> 00:21:43,310
If it can be realized,

384
00:21:43,640 --> 00:21:45,030
without Jiang Jie's help,

385
00:21:45,110 --> 00:21:47,070
Jiang Xiu will forgive you.

386
00:22:02,680 --> 00:22:04,440
(Something came up all of a sudden.)

387
00:22:04,590 --> 00:22:06,070
(Next time we're on day-off,)

388
00:22:06,070 --> 00:22:08,590
(I'll definitely accompany you
to do what you wanna do together.)

389
00:22:12,200 --> 00:22:13,400
Hello, Jingjing.

390
00:22:13,590 --> 00:22:15,720
(Chef, help me take care of my child.)

391
00:22:21,340 --> 00:22:24,780
(Xijiangyue)

392
00:22:25,680 --> 00:22:26,310
We need to talk.

393
00:22:27,480 --> 00:22:28,750
The lunch time is about to start.

394
00:22:29,440 --> 00:22:30,590
Let's talk after that.

395
00:22:38,400 --> 00:22:39,750
Your child?

396
00:22:40,480 --> 00:22:42,480
- Your birth child?
- Of course.

397
00:22:42,720 --> 00:22:44,480
You're married?

398
00:22:44,480 --> 00:22:46,400
And your child is already so big.

399
00:22:48,830 --> 00:22:50,110
It's a long story.

400
00:22:50,350 --> 00:22:51,480
I have plenty of time.

401
00:22:54,960 --> 00:22:56,480
Anyway,

402
00:22:56,640 --> 00:22:57,920
my ex-husband suddenly died.

403
00:22:58,110 --> 00:22:59,350
Now I need to go to his funeral.

404
00:22:59,350 --> 00:23:01,480
My dad is abroad. So...

405
00:23:01,640 --> 00:23:04,240
I need you to take care of my child.

406
00:23:05,240 --> 00:23:06,960
But I've never
taken care of a child before.

407
00:23:07,440 --> 00:23:09,640
Didn't you babysit your dad before?
It's more or less the same.

408
00:23:10,920 --> 00:23:12,200
Look at her! How adorable!

409
00:23:12,400 --> 00:23:13,640
Zaizai, say hi to this lady.

410
00:23:13,750 --> 00:23:15,510
Hello.

411
00:23:16,270 --> 00:23:19,920
Don't you want to experience what it'll
be like after you marry Jiang Jie?

412
00:23:20,310 --> 00:23:22,960
- How did you know this?
- I'm not blind.

413
00:23:23,960 --> 00:23:25,680
Don't you mind it?

414
00:23:25,790 --> 00:23:27,030
Why would I mind it?

415
00:23:27,070 --> 00:23:28,550
As long as you pay me the salary on time,

416
00:23:28,550 --> 00:23:30,510
just be with anyone as you like.

417
00:23:31,720 --> 00:23:33,240
Fine, just leave this kid to me.

418
00:23:34,270 --> 00:23:35,550
Zaizai, call me gorgeous.

419
00:23:35,960 --> 00:23:36,830
Aunt Nai.

420
00:23:37,310 --> 00:23:38,160
Gorgeous.

421
00:23:38,880 --> 00:23:40,750
- Aunt Nai.
- Gorgeous. Gorgeous.

422
00:23:40,830 --> 00:23:41,750
Call me gorgeous.

423
00:23:48,400 --> 00:23:49,960
I need to go back by car. I can't drink.

424
00:23:50,160 --> 00:23:50,790
Let's drink this.

425
00:24:04,000 --> 00:24:05,240
How did he threaten you?

426
00:24:09,640 --> 00:24:10,920
Can't it be my voluntary choice?

427
00:24:11,270 --> 00:24:13,350
- You wouldn't.
- Like I said,

428
00:24:14,000 --> 00:24:15,750
we're taking two different paths.

429
00:24:17,030 --> 00:24:18,000
So, I would.

430
00:24:18,400 --> 00:24:19,750
Did you forget why your father

431
00:24:19,750 --> 00:24:21,550
left Xijiangyue back then?

432
00:24:21,920 --> 00:24:23,350
Did you forget what he had suffered?

433
00:24:23,680 --> 00:24:24,640
All I remember

434
00:24:24,640 --> 00:24:26,640
is he worked for the Jiang family
as the Sous Chef all his life.

435
00:24:26,720 --> 00:24:28,790
And he was forced to be
Jiang Yuanfeng's substitute.

436
00:24:29,110 --> 00:24:31,240
Afterward, he only wanted to open
his own restaurant.

437
00:24:31,270 --> 00:24:33,469
But he was suppressed by Jiang Yuanfeng
and had to stop being a chef.

438
00:24:36,030 --> 00:24:37,440
Just because I remember all of that,

439
00:24:38,720 --> 00:24:40,030
I joined Xijiangyue.

440
00:24:40,440 --> 00:24:42,640
Jiang Xuyang promised you
the position of Head Chef?

441
00:24:46,680 --> 00:24:48,160
You're making the same mistake.

442
00:24:49,350 --> 00:24:51,400
Do you know what he's up to?

443
00:24:51,720 --> 00:24:53,030
He and Cui Jing

444
00:24:53,200 --> 00:24:54,640
plan to open the restaurants in Baichuan

445
00:24:54,750 --> 00:24:56,720
across the country in the form
of chain restaurants.

446
00:24:57,270 --> 00:24:59,240
In his eyes, a chef is merely

447
00:24:59,240 --> 00:25:01,160
a tool that can be replaced anytime.

448
00:25:02,640 --> 00:25:03,790
It's none of my business.

449
00:25:04,680 --> 00:25:06,440
Jiang Jie, do you think you're awesome?

450
00:25:07,030 --> 00:25:08,750
Without you and Chuncheng,

451
00:25:09,000 --> 00:25:10,720
I can be a Chef anyway.

452
00:25:10,880 --> 00:25:13,160
This is what the Jiang family
owes my family.

453
00:25:37,030 --> 00:25:40,000
Jiang Jie, you're finally back.

454
00:25:40,000 --> 00:25:42,160
You're finally back.

455
00:25:42,830 --> 00:25:46,110
Hello. Come here. Get up. Get up.

456
00:25:47,440 --> 00:25:49,030
Li Nai, who is this?

457
00:25:49,030 --> 00:25:51,110
Jiang Jie, I don't know your door code.

458
00:25:51,400 --> 00:25:53,880
Jiang Jie, I don't know your door code.

459
00:25:55,310 --> 00:25:57,030
Which question is more important now?

460
00:25:57,270 --> 00:26:00,920
I don't know your door code.

461
00:26:13,030 --> 00:26:15,440
(010, the door is unlocked.)

462
00:26:17,510 --> 00:26:18,310
Our love anniversary?

463
00:26:20,240 --> 00:26:21,270
Childish!

464
00:26:23,790 --> 00:26:25,350
- Are you happy?
- Yes.

465
00:26:28,720 --> 00:26:31,070
- What's wrong?
- We've got a kid here.

466
00:26:31,790 --> 00:26:32,920
So what?

467
00:26:33,640 --> 00:26:34,550
You haven't told me yet.

468
00:26:36,550 --> 00:26:38,590
She's Jingjing's daughter, Zaizai.

469
00:26:38,830 --> 00:26:40,310
Jingjing's child?

470
00:26:41,240 --> 00:26:42,550
I wanna fly a kite.

471
00:26:53,720 --> 00:26:55,310
This kite is of poor quality.

472
00:26:55,350 --> 00:26:56,790
Aunt Nai, you can't fly it.

473
00:26:57,070 --> 00:26:58,590
I'm Gorgeous.

474
00:27:00,640 --> 00:27:02,440
I'll take her to fly the kite. Zaizai.

475
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:04,270
- I'll take you to fly the kite.
- Okay.

476
00:27:06,070 --> 00:27:06,920
Take a rest over there.

477
00:27:08,200 --> 00:27:09,750
Aunt Nai is so childish.

478
00:27:12,030 --> 00:27:13,200
It's Gorgeous.

