00:27:42,020 --> 00:27:43,780
♪Pursue forward♪

486
00:27:43,940 --> 00:27:46,320
♪Snuggle back to back♪

487
00:27:46,580 --> 00:27:50,820
♪Turn around and you'll be mine♪

488
00:27:51,020 --> 00:27:52,780
♪To face up♪

489
00:27:52,980 --> 00:27:55,340
♪Every single rose♪

