493
00:28:08,460 --> 00:28:10,860
♪Snuggle back to back♪

494
00:28:11,100 --> 00:28:15,380
♪Turn around and you'll be mine♪

495
00:28:15,540 --> 00:28:17,300
♪To face up♪

496
00:28:18,110 --> 00:28:19,960
