499
00:28:27,420 --> 00:28:29,580
♪One look and my heart misses a beat♪

500
00:28:29,830 --> 00:28:31,510
I... I'm thirsty too.

501
00:28:33,700 --> 00:28:36,260
♪I guess I'm a little flipped♪

502
00:28:36,460 --> 00:28:39,100
