530
00:30:54,750 --> 00:30:57,440
Coincidentally, Mr. Jiang will celebrate
his 70th birthday.

531
00:30:57,750 --> 00:31:01,110
This year's Alliance Meeting will be held
in the form of a dinner party.

532
00:31:01,270 --> 00:31:05,350
Li Nai, Chef of Eating at Dusk,
is cordially invited to the event.

533
00:31:05,920 --> 00:31:08,480
The Alliance Meeting and Jiang Ziqing's
birthday party are held on the same day.

534
00:31:08,640 --> 00:31:10,160
I smelt a rat.

535
00:31:10,790 --> 00:31:14,510
Jiang Ziqing must wanna take the chance
to enhance the seven families' position.

536
00:31:14,720 --> 00:31:16,720
